  <XDFCONSTANT uniqueid="0x110">
    <title>Checksum Word @ 0x800C</title>
    <description>16-bit big-endian checksum word. Stock value is 0x4A65; MOD2 value is 0x47BE. This word is the one's complement of the checksum complement word at 0x800E.</description>
