  <XDFCONSTANT uniqueid="0x114">
    <title>MOD2 Changed Last Cell of 0x8B41 Bank @ 0x8C18</title>
    <description>Single byte changed by MOD2 from 0x38 to 0x3C. Disassembly of the 0x48EE routine shows this is row 23 column 8 of the 24x9 bank at 0x8B41, not a separate adjacent vector.</description>
