  <XDFTABLE uniqueid="0x22D" flags="0x30">
    <title>Load / Air-Charge Model Factor 24x9 @ 0x9187</title>
    <description>Medium-high structural confidence view for the code-confirmed 0x9187 24x9 lookup. The routine at 0x6344 builds a B2D6 descriptor at RAM 0x218D, derives one axis through helper 0xB383 using vector 0x9291 and count/stride byte 0x929A=9, loads the second axis from RPM-like RAM 0x2036, sets base 0x9187, and returns the interpolated byte. Known callers store the result at RAM 0x210F and RAM 0x00D0; one path then stores 0x00CE = 0x00D0 left-shifted by 2, feeding the 0x2034 load/MAP-like axis used by the spark maps. Values display with X / 230. Best current role is upstream load/air-charge modelling into 0x00D0/0x00CE/0x2034; not main fuel.</description>
    <CATEGORYMEM index="0" category="6" />
    <XDFAXIS id="x" uniqueid="0x0"><EMBEDDEDDATA mmedelementsizebits="8" mmedmajorstridebits="0" mmedminorstridebits="0" /><indexcount>9</indexcount><datatype>0</datatype><unittype>0</unittype><DALINK index="0" /><LABEL index="0" value="0" /><LABEL index="1" value="3" /><LABEL index="2" value="11" /><LABEL index="3" value="22" /><LABEL index="4" value="37" /><LABEL index="5" value="54" /><LABEL index="6" value="89" /><LABEL index="7" value="132" /><LABEL index="8" value="201" /><MATH equation="X"><VAR id="X" /></MATH></XDFAXIS>
